Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小就有一个疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么只能是「我」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是「他人」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我思 故我在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先哲如是说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这「思」的对象从自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转向了他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那个人 是否也是我？」
