Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「思他人」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一思 我就变成了他人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最多只有五秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转眼间 我就变回了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这期间 本来的我会失去意识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还因此而受伤多次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再者 我只能入侵视野范围内的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故而无法行淫邪之事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多只能入侵讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向周围寻衅 再抽身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能耐 只能如此用来撒气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账 想死啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不识相的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 我终于
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到了充分利用这项异能的良策
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五分钟后交卷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断入侵班里的聪明人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记下答案 回来答题 如此反复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 我的目标是进名校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 考高中与平日的小考不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考场之中 不知谁聪明谁笨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 我走进各大升学培训班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装成培训生 一次次地入内刺探
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个人想考哪所高中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长哪门功课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都调查得清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我锁定了数名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我报考相同高中的聪明人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功考进了名校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是新生代表致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙坂有宇同学 请上台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是新生状元吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还是个帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们新生举办如此隆重的典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.64,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,在这春光明媚的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.28,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走进了传统名校阳野森高中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.71,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,在新的学习生活中 我们将刻苦学习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:36.93,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,积极参加学校与社团活动 提高自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是你喜欢的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小弓你也对上眼了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次感谢在座的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.74,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\be2\frz12\pos(1731,560)}突然致信 多有打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.74,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\be2\frz12\pos(1747,647)\b0}我是1-2班的杉本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.74,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\be2\frz12\pos(1768,735)\b0}放学后，能请你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.74,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\be2\frz12\pos(1796,821)\b0}来教学楼后面一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.74,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\be2\frz12\pos(1816,910)\b0}我会一直等到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在学习年级第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人长得也帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不受青睐都不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦 趁早处理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳你跑这么一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 找我有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问！你愿意和我做朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 和我交往吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了保持现在的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须废寝忘食地学习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有时间去陪别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爷我根本不学习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打搅 真的很抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能看得上你们这些普通妹子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 小弓你没看昨天的特别篇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是本校的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白柳 弓！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你…攻下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会必将降临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力最多持续五秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键在于运用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.85,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直看到深夜 结果早上起不来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.73,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,挣扎了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三三 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫警察
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真险 好在计划成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才可真险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弓 你差点被卡车撞到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他 是1班的乙坂救了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没受伤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去医务室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走得动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其…其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本来想去常去的店…吃松饼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能请你…同去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友去吃才开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里！你是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好好答谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想和你多聊聊天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀有电话 喂哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那我马上回去 嗯嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三三 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那京都的哥哥突然回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给家里每人订了份特级寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就…你俩去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演技真假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你这助攻还不错 三囧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等 吃法有讲究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请学我的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样弄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖汁能浸透得更彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后再叠起来 切开来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到换个吃法 就能变得这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闻所未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百吃不厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放的曲子 是哈罗哈罗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.72,note3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1138,985)}How-Low-Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 哈罗哈罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听说过吗 我还以为男生都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在流行这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后能再请你和我放学后走走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃点东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.20,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\b0\frz11.4\pos(1333,664)}今天放学后也一起走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.20,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\b0\frz11.4\pos(1433,728)}我在大门口等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 笑出声来可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高一1班 乙坂有宇同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请马上来学生会室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.12,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.69,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,高一1班 乙坂有宇同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.91,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,请马上来学生会室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.60,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs66\be1\b0\pos(1415,284)\frz12}抱歉 我晚点到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.60,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\b0\be1\frz12\t(0,130,0.7,\fs66)\move(690,840,836,814,0,130)}我等你{\c&HA380EB&}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是学生会长 大村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面有人在等我 请你快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快不快取决于你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你上次摸底考试答卷的复印件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无懈可击的满分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的考卷摆在你桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你在这里 再拿一次满分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有作弊的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拿90分以上就排除嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿不到 那就是作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无理取闹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事已获得校长与教导主任的批准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果逃走 你将被直接退学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退 退学！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请答卷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全套答案就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能入侵他 获取答案了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍人呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见你自己撕了那些纸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是学生会长 友利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不是你们学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 一直在这里拍你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看刚才拍的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没有看他撕答卷纸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才却说你看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再给你看些别的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你具有入侵他人的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在使用能力作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是嗜睡病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时睡意会突然向我袭来 我无法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你体检报告的复印件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这上面…根本没写什么嗜睡病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 答卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这种鬼把戏…我不奉陪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 算准了会这样是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来轮到我上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起来 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我没事…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子…到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间移动？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间移动 就是在刹那间完成移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我无法精确地刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个能力 我不知进了多少次医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能力的缺陷也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说 你想对我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你转学到我们学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上除你之外 还有许多特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一种出现在青春期的「病」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在能力消失前 请你在我们星海学园上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经获得了你监护人的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 靠这张脸就能走桃花运了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要拼命作弊来添个秀才的高帽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不过你靠这个泡到了心仪的妹子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消 消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是她的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…隐身能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我看到了她揍你的全过程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…只有我没看见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 她的能力能让她不被单个对象认知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了那个对象 其他人都能看见她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是个有缺陷的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你要加入我们学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力很有用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协什么助？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓吓那些像你一样乱用能力的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 就是这样一群人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 有宇哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你的脸怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体育课上出了点…问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦对啦 叔叔来电话了 大新闻的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说我和有宇哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以转进星海学园初中部和高中部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免学费哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来真的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 经济负担减轻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔还说 会送好吃的过来当贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 连你也要转学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你舍得离开你的朋友们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的智能机可以视频通话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下并无太多不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的晚饭是…锵！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有宇哥哥最爱吃的蛋包饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b0\bord2\an8\fad(300,0)}（可喜可贺）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过多少次了 我小时候才喜欢吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可喜可贺！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭里还加披萨酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候的我 才会喜欢这种甜味吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没吃妈妈做的蛋包饭了 好想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种人 就别提她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还生她的气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在离婚后把我们塞给了叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过希望你能原谅她的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家 只有你我二人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢 我有时会觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我们家还有过一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们兄妹俩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是做梦梦到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得现实中也有过 好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 明天要搬家 要早起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再给在下些许时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 还真喜欢看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里望去 能看到人类去不了的远方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这实在是很了不起的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 在学校里别开口闭口谈星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被疏远的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问这又是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经验之谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用人生经历告诉你 不能聊星星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该聊昨晚的电视节目 这才是王道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经验之谈？王道？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂就算了 快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房间好宽敞的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和有宇哥哥真的可以独占这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区在下 愿效微劳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工人大哥会做好的 不用帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我能帮上一点忙…不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别抢别人的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦！没能想到这一层呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 到底出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我要转去星海学园了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个…说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在能力消失之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止我去监视不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果白柳同学能来见我 我会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 实在是太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能每周一次 你来我往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也…抱歉 我不能来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来话长…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事 是严禁外传的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在是无能为力…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢的心情货真价实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我并没有和你开始交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 如果单方面追随离去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不就成跟踪狂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 我也很惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我没法来见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后 我们就各走各路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 我会记住你这个救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远感恩在心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我要在此向你道别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保重身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本…本小爷…被甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说正在打扰～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然来我家干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家两个人 人手不足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？两位是有宇哥哥新学校的同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我们来自学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫高城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是友利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们放学了 正好过来帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意帮把手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 帮大忙了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 分头干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是步未说的…叔叔送的贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「好吃的」东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋全是金叔拉面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当没看见好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步未妹妹 变魔术看不看？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 很想看的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了 说变就变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！诶诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比电视上的人还厉害的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用能力来玩耍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你把步未吓的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来玩的么 那请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对好心的帮手还这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了我做的晚饭再走也不迟的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里没那么多碗筷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 哈罗哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真流行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 西森柚咲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不亦可爱乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.62,0:23:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的歌也能大卖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界真是没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的新学校 就在有宇哥哥旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想一起上学的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会被人当成妹控的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹控？遥控大赛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 星海学园 这名字真好听的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就像是为你而起的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这天晚上 我做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是听了步未突发奇想的话 受了影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁来着
