Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.95,0:24:44.72,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,250)}吹走心中迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.03,0:24:48.67,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}世界尽头的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.71,0:24:52.30,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我们竟不知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.40,0:24:55.99,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}生命中的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.11,0:24:59.68,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}竟也无法摈弃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.78,0:25:03.33,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}继续向前走去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.45,0:25:07.10,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}终能寻获勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.20,0:25:10.67,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}梦却向我预示
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.81,0:25:14.46,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}寻获既是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:18.17,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}天空改貌换颜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.23,0:25:21.89,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}群星流转不息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:25.57,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待到梦醒之后
